Subterranean [3bc edit] Chuck Biscuits / Kosmic
Back again with a respin on an old theme, here's a remix of my kosmic debut, mixed up for the floor! (bewm bewm) Samples are from the original as well as a korg ms 10.
Hmm... Do i do nothing but remixes now ? :) Bogo greets go out to diode, cd YOU ROCK, ani, skie, base, MS, #trax, and ShadowH (CURRY)
Base: hmm, how's this for selling out to the floor huh ? :) The name of this track is now a complete misnomer !
